trans-unit.resname: KidRun is an application used for establishments school for their cross in order to start the race, to scan their QR-CODE to record the student's time by doing automatic classification by classes and by gender.
trans-unit.source: KidRun is an application used for establishments school for their cross in order to start the race, to scan their QR-CODE to record the student's time by doing automatic classification by classes and by gender.
trans-unit.target: KidRun est une application utilisée pour des établissements scolaires pour leur cross afin de démarrer la course, de scanner leur QR-CODE pour enregistrer le chrono de l'élève en faisant automatiquement un classement par classes et par genre.
